-- Yuan Change `Constructive Gesture,' Former EU Trade Chief Mandelson Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-26T06:21:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-26/yuan-change-constructive-gesture-former-eu-trade-chief-mandelson-says.html

          
          
             China’s decision to end the yuan’s
peg against the dollar is a “constructive gesture” that will
reduce trade tensions and contribute towards a rebalancing of
the economy, Peter Mandelson, former EU Commissioner for Trade,
said in a financial forum in Shanghai.  
